# New Webhook

Create a new webhook to receive notifications (like reminders) at an external URL.

## [Actions](<%= base_path %>/new/actions)

* [`create_webhook(url, name, events)`](<%= base_path %>/new/actions/create_webhook) - Create a new webhook

## Parameters

| Parameter | Type | Required | Description |
|-----------|------|----------|-------------|
| url | string | yes | The HTTPS URL to receive webhook payloads |
| name | string | no | A descriptive name for this webhook |
| events | array | no | Event types to subscribe to (default: notifications.delivered) |

## Available Event Types

| Event Type | Description |
|------------|-------------|
| `notifications.delivered` | Any notification was delivered (includes reminders, mentions, comments, etc.) |
| `reminders.delivered` | A scheduled reminder was delivered (subset of notifications) |

